Exact cause is unconfirmed. The current page state suggests that the petition page remains live while the starter-account identity layer may have been anonymized, detached, partially removed, or degraded at the presentation level.

## Recommended Governance Treatment

- Treat the page as a live third-party petition incident.
- Track the degraded starter identity block as a distinct presentation-layer condition.
- Do not classify the incident as resolved solely because the starter profile appears degraded.
- Distinguish this incident from both dead-link incidents and fully intact live profile incidents.

